# Login Server Popup - UI Specification

## Layout
Modal popup: 600px wide, max-height 80vh, centered on screen with dark overlay backdrop.

## Component Breakdown

### Header Section
- Server name (text-2xl, bold)
- Close button (top-right X icon, hover effect)
- Background: gradient or solid accent color

### Banner Section
- Full-width image (aspect 16:9, max-height 200px)
- Fallback: gradient background if no banner
- Object-fit: cover

### Server Time Display
- Label: "Server Time"
- Format: HH:MM:SS (24-hour, with timezone abbreviation)
- Update every second
- Style: monospace font, subtle background

### MOTD Section
- Label: "Message of the Day"
- Markdown support for basic formatting
- Max 300 characters, scrollable if longer
- Style: card with light background

### Welcome Message Section
- Label: "Welcome!"
- Personalized text with user's name
- Markdown support
- Style: distinct from MOTD (different color/border)

## Styling Notes
- Use existing theme colors (from theme store)
- Smooth fade-in animation (200ms)
- Responsive: stack vertically on mobile
- Use Tailwind utilities for consistency